text: Arthur Noyes may refer to: * Arthur Amos Noyes (1866–1936), American chemist, inventor and educator * Arthur Noyes (organist) (1862–1929), church organist in South Australia * Arthur Percy Noyes (1880–1963), psychiatric administrator and educator * Arthur H. Noyes (1853–1915), U.S. federal judge
title: Arthur Noyes
